channel.title: JSRevolution...The Revolution Is Here
channel.description:
Hello! And Welcome To The Last Server You Will Ever Play! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------ Dont You Just HATE All Those Stupid Project Czar Servers... Ive Analysed The Mopar Server Status Page...And 90% Are Czar Base. 80% Are Un-Edited Project Czar And The Rest Are Ussally ****.
Lets Face It. Most Popular Servers Out There...
The Original google...(Not A Fan.) But Its Popular Non The Less. Frugoo Scape...(Not My Cup Of Tea, But Seems Popular) ZDR..(Before The Realease)
Now..I Got SICK Of All These Servers...I Wanted To Play A Server...Where I didnt Get 126 In 2 Mins And When I Went Pking, Admins 1 Hit Me. And I Got SICK Of Playing A Server For 2 Days..Then Its Suddenly Down Forever.
All I Wanted, Is To Be Able To Work For My Levels...Pk In Real Wilderness...Train Real Skills...And Not Have to Keep Restarting On New Servers...Over and Over.
If Your Like Me...Your In The Right Place...
As I Present To You....[b]JSRevolution[/b] -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Before The Pics...I Take 0 Credit For Any Work On This Server, Because If I Do Throw Credit To Myself, i'll Get People Saying "Leecher" "Noob" Etc.
So 100% Credit To All The People Out There Who Contributed To The Runescape Private Server Communties.
[b] Features [/b]
- 90% Real Runescape Wilderness. (Levels, Attacking Timers, Teleblock) - Perfect Specials For.. (DDS, D Long, D Mace, Whip, D Halberd, D Spear, Mage Short) - Specials For G Maul, Etc. - Skill Cape Emotes. - Emotes. - Working Teleports ( Use Them To Get Around) - Run On Dedicated - Up 24 / 7 (NO Im Not Just Saying That..It Should Be Up Most The Time Unless Updating) - Lag Free...Lag Free Until About 100+ People. - God Wars Mini-Game With Rewards And Reward Shop! - Multiple Training Areas - Multiple Pking Areas - Barrows (With Random Rewards Depending On Kills) - Moving Fire Capes - Coloured Money - Full Range - Full Mage w/ Runes - Prayer Icons w/ Effects
[b] Skills [ /b]
- Herblore - Fletching - Firemaking - Slayer - With Tasks - Runecrafting w/ Ess Mining - Mining - Smithing - Smelting - Crafting - Woodcutting - Theiving - Prayer w/ Icons & Effects - Full Range w/ Projectiles, Graphics, Etc. - Full Mage w/ Runes. - Main Combat Skills. (Attack, Strength, Defence, Hitpoints,)
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
A Few Handy Tips.
[b] - To Get Around To Places USE MAGIC TELEPORTS, You Know, The Things In The Magic Book, Varrock Tele Etc. - Actually Use The ::help Cos Its Not There For No Reason. [/b]
For Guides...
Visit Forums, JSRevolution Section, Guides.
i'll Post Link To Forums, Once Beta Testing Is Finished And Realeased Publicly.
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

And Theres Much Much More...So Come Along...And Join...The Revolution.
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
[b]NOTE: IF YOU WANT 126 IN A FEW MINS OR CANT BE BOTHERED TRAINING THIS IS NOT THE SERVER FOR YOU!!!! NOTE: THIS SERVER WILL TAKE ATLEAST A FEW HOURS OF TRAINING FOR 1 SKILL IN 99 IF YOU DO NOT WANT THAT DO NOT COME HERE!!!! NOTE: IF YOU JUST WANT TO COME TO SPAM AND SWEAR YOU WILL BE PERM IP BANNED AND WONT BE ABLE TO ENJOY THE SERVER!!![/b]
We Have A ZERO Tolerance For Spamming / Flamming / Advertising.
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
This Server Does Need A Client, Which I Will Post The Link For Once We Realease Publicly.
THIS IS IN THE RIGHT SECTION! It Is The "HELP / [b]DEVELOPMENT[/b] SECTION" And This Is My Developments!
